{"tid":2104303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族等三小時搶閘撐35+   選民誓「攞返主導權」","createTime":"2020-07-12T00:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T00:32:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c2fa3abc472aafcab47e8eb6f688451314bea0","tid":2104303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/DEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FDEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7bb05d57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FDEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA%2F&h=84e5babc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/DEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銀髮族等三小時搶閘撐35+  <br />\n選民誓「攞返主導權」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【投票不投降】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】排長龍打蛇餅盛況，繼去年11.24區選後再現各區，不少選民昨午9時便到初選票站等候，以投下支持進軍9月立法會換屆選舉的民主派代表。銀髮族為了投票，不惜苦候三小時，表明不因政府稱初選違法而卻步；年輕選民不滿當局打壓不絕，勢以選票表達反對意志堅定。不少市民擔心這是港版國安法後最後一次公平選舉，恐防日後表達自由亦被削，故珍惜還有的投票機會，支持民主派「35+」搶灘，在街頭外雙線抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n昨天各區所見，不少票站都有銀髮族排隊，89歲的九西選民龐婆婆上午9時、即票站開始前三小時，已撐着枴杖到石硤尾票站排首位投票，她稱不擔心初選被指違法，「自己做返自己嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wKPIpjdsJ3ZYoJ83gShWxUi8O_I=/709x702/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H62Q2Q52IT5ZH7DUIK5WYATHNA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwKPIpjdsJ3ZYoJ83gShWxUi8O_I%3D%2F709x702%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH62Q2Q52IT5ZH7DUIK5WYATHNA.gif&h=5c8d8eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yqRXJvxlr3REj8D6L8d685U6T3E=/340x289/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SVFJEOW53I47OGNNTALA7MQZ2A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyqRXJvxlr3REj8D6L8d685U6T3E%3D%2F340x289%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSVFJEOW53I47OGNNTALA7MQZ2A.gif&h=9a37dabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃店老闆娘陳太：「無論乜嘢階級、乜嘢人，你真係做得到，就做囉！如果今次都做唔到嘅話，可能嚟緊都冇呢個選舉㗎喇，所以我覺得要堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gYmEuf-3QgiQg3t-5feHQoyxqkg=/340x289/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WOJGZNPIFKHUSWTMQZLWI37ASE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgYmEuf-3QgiQg3t-5feHQoyxqkg%3D%2F340x289%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWOJGZNPIFKHUSWTMQZLWI37ASE.gif&h=60f1471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n義工情侶姚先生及馮小姐：「幫得就幫，可能下次冇機會（初選），或者變中國式選舉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OsggUyerzX4aXigHCe-P6AxZ_uQ=/340x289/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RZWJ7QMYXF5INEUOLDAGWRZH2A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOsggUyerzX4aXigHCe-P6AxZ_uQ%3D%2F340x289%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRZWJ7QMYXF5INEUOLDAGWRZH2A.gif&h=fea1391c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九東選民Helen：「噚晚研究所被搜電腦，曾經擔心今日無法投票；見到仲有咁多人願意行出嚟，就算有冇用都好，出嚟投票係對得住自己。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店無懼打壓 借舖做票站<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警查票站影市民 製白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n在港島區，快將65歲、自言是泛民支持者的林先生也於上午9時已到票站，稱等候三小時只為票投年輕人；被問到會否擔心年輕參選人最終被取消資格？他指「初選無所謂」，「推咗後生仔入去先，畀佢哋試下。」<br />\n<br />\n「我哋支持35+，畀我哋攞返個主導權！」嚴氏一家昨到屯門市中心新<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n國際社會才會看到港人的意志：「要畀國際社會睇到香港人仲喺度！」<br />\n<br />\n九西選民楊先生也到荔枝角<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n：「越打壓就越需要嚟支持，我哋係需要民主」，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n：「唔好理成功率高唔高，每樣嘢都唔做，就唔會有人成功。」<br />\n<br />\n不少黃店亦有參與其中，借出店舖作票站，包括位處傳統「藍區」大角咀的黃店「餃子店」。該店老闆娘陳太指，港版國安法壓頂，借舖前也曾擔心，但她相信更加多人比自己更恐懼，笑謂：「我諗未打到嚟嘅，我哋照做咗先啦！」<br />\n<br />\n陳太指出，民<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，所以我覺得要堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義工憂下次變中國式選舉<br />\n<br />\n在石硤尾票站有情侶檔義工齊以行動支持初選。從事IT的80後姚先生指，今次是第一次做選舉活動義工：「幫得就幫，可能下次冇機會（初選）」，估計未來香港選舉或變「中國式選舉」；其90後女朋友、醫護學生馮小姐也指，投票在香港一直是合法，對政府宣稱初選違法感到荒謬，強調自己支持普世價值，投票是重要的自由。"},{"pid":"5f6624bc8d29b8aa3b5185107907b0fba7b08887","tid":2104303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2400cfeb44d0e473b2f99590db72ddb23d23511","tid":2104303,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人都未明什麼是南柯一夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235164ac66c614b599859bca0666ac4ca8478b89","tid":2104303,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c2fa3abc472aafcab47e8eb6f688451314bea0","tid":2104303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/DEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FDEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7bb05d57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2FDEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA%2F&h=84e5babc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/DEKK22N2F44IY4GTEOUMOPFUBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銀髮族等三小時搶閘撐35+  <br />\n選民誓「攞返主導權」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【投票不投降】<br />\